{"tid":1779582,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"【無聊post】五毛同藍絲嘅新稱呼：家畜","createTime":"2019-12-11T18:43:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-11T18:43:59.000Z","uid":56239,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"fcc43d8c11067fab945f1023e2bd16ec486eb16e","tid":1779582,"uid":56239,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:43:19.000Z","msg":"對哩班唔係失智就係跌咗良心嘅生物，我諗咗好耐用咩名詞形容佢地而又唔侮辱到其他動物，最後諗到我地嘅巨人（sorry手頭得殘體字版）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eR1hPjv.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeR1hPjv.png&h=3676c7cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n被佢地黑暴，暴徒，曱甴叫得咁開心，畀多個選擇大家簡潔咁回敬佢地：<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">家畜</span></span><br />\n<br />\n冇話兩腳行走嘅靈長類唔可以做家畜，所以只會委屈一下可愛嘅豬牛羊雞鴨鵝加多一類同伴，而唔會侮辱到佢地本身<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n叫佢地返大陸/大灣區，可以改做叫佢地<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">返豬圈食同類</span></span>（再度委屈一下豬豬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）<br />\n<br />\n當然未來大家主要精力要放返喺對抗中共嘅分化，但有時上網見哩類生物想直接侮辱下佢地，用厭咗五毛可以用下哩個，冇乜違和感。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fec9e4aac35c9448152a8c1bff10160f3743cfb9","tid":1779582,"uid":294221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:43:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ow4Z2BY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fow4Z2BY.jpg&h=1345ec69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人最強後盾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/addoiluk1023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddoiluk1023&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=aa71b8ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addoiluk1023</a>"},{"pid":"f5dbbf4c904c83d2e7f5880b9c1fb6857aab0c15","tid":1779582,"uid":294221,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-11T18:43:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ow4Z2BY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fow4Z2BY.jpg&h=1345ec69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">香港人最強後盾</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://t.me/addoiluk1023\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Faddoiluk1023&d=WPWOQTheSiAT%2FB2p9vAnAG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=aa71b8ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/addoiluk1023</a>"}]}